snippet.title: 🔥🔥🦒Castle on the Coast🦒🔥🔥 - Parkouring Giraffe????
snippet.description:
🦒 PC: bit.ly/COTC-steam
🦒 NS: bit.ly/COTC-ns
🦒 PS: bit.ly/COTC-ns
🦒 Xbox: bit.ly/COTC-xbox

🔥 A cute giraffe with extreme parkour powers!? This giraffe can get anywhere, anytime!
🔥 Parkour through a magic castle as George the Giraffe!
🔥 Help George explore the magical castle, home to crystal caverns, stone-laden halls, and trippy alternate dimensions. 
🔥 Seamlessly wander from level to level with no loading screens in a large, interconnected world.

🐿️🐿️🐿️ A nutty sidekick joins the mix (co-op mode). Player 2 can control George's sidekick: Swirlz, the flying squirrel!
